1
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,730
How could you

2
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:19,560
just forget about me?

3
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,630
I want to see

4
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:32,920
where exactly

5
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,360
you are injured.

6
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,860
What are you doing?

7
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:08,760
You...

8
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,800
You just said you had a headache.

9
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,120
Why are you here?

10
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,640
You got drunk last night,

11
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,710
so

12
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,240
I sent you back.

13
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:23,240
I was afraid you would feel unwell,

14
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:23,590
so...

15
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,410
so I stayed by your side.

16
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,470
You stayed with me all night?

17
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,680
If there's nothing else,

18
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,240
I'll leave first.

19
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:38,990
You...

20
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,750
keep sleeping. Go ahead.

21
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,870
How did I get drunk again yesterday?

22
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,150
Yesterday,

23
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,600
there was some kind of banquet.

24
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:17,550
It seems they said
Xiao Chi is going to the capital.

25
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,630
So it seems

26
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:22,070
we have no choice but to obey
the decree and return to the capital.

27
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:22,920
For now,

28
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,760
Her Highness seems fine,

29
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,480
but the female official
with her knows martial arts.

30
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,190
Is she going back to the capital with us?

31
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,390
There's no other way.

32
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,940
If we don't let her follow,

33
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,300
Her Highness will surely be displeased.

34
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:35,270
General Xiao.

35
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,120
If you have something to discuss,

36
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,320
I'll come back later.

37
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,030
It's fine.

38
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,750
Physician Han,
if you have something to say,

39
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:48,480
just say it.

40
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:51,920
Oh.

41
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,860
Then I'll go out first.

42
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,070
No need.

43
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,840
You guys talk.

44
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,600
I heard you are going to the capital.

45
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,720
Yes.

46
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,080
When will you leave?

47
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,120
In 3 days.

48
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:24,720
Then...

49
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:27,390
Then what if you get sick?

50
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,200
Military orders

51
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,340
must be obeyed.

52
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,270
But with your treatment during this time,

53
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,870
I'm much better now.

54
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:41,720
But I...

55
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:46,190
If the treatment is interrupted

56
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:49,120
and the illness recurs,
the condition will grow far worse.

57
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,560
There's not much time left.

58
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,159
I can't worry about that much.

59
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:52,600
I...

60
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,580
Physician Han,

61
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,830
after I leave,

62
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:59,200
what are your plans?

63
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:00,370
Once you leave,

64
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,880
what's the point of
my staying in this city?

65
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,460
I'm going back to Changmo.

66
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:11,680
Okay.

67
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,330
At that time,

68
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,510
I will have someone
prepare your medical fees

69
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,710
and more gifts for you

70
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,750
to take back.

71
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,950
Who needs your gifts?

72
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:27,310
Tonight, I will give you
acupuncture for the last time,

73
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,830
then you go back to the capital,

74
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:30,360
and I'll go back to Changmo.

75
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,440
Seven years ago,

76
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,800
you came here with me,

77
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:42,590
leaving our homes and families behind,

78
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:45,560
shedding our blood outside Tianlang Pass,

79
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,860
because Tianlang Pass

80
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:49,000
is the most important place in Jinglan.

81
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,870
Behind us are our families

82
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,510
and the thousands of citizens of Jinglan.

83
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,170
Therefore,

84
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,430
even if we die in battle,

85
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:56,510
we absolutely can't retreat!

86
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:58,190
-You're right!
-You're right!

87
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,680
After I escort Her Highness
back to the capital,

88
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,950
I will return as soon as possible.

89
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:01,950
During this time,

90
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,830
all affairs

91
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,830
will be temporarily handled by Lu Li.

92
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,690
You must report everything to her

93
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,070
and follow her arrangements.

94
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:08,730
-Yes!
-Yes!

95
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,720
Report!

96
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,450
General,

97
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,730
Her Highness is ill.

98
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:22,760
She was fine yesterday.

99
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,170
Why is she ill today?

100
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,240
How is it?

101
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,630
Judging by Her Highness's complexion,

102
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,360
it seems she ate something bad.

103
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,830
Ate something bad?

104
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,870
Perhaps it's because,
having traveled a long way,

105
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:40,070
Her Highness is weary

106
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:42,680
and is unaccustomed to the climate.

107
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,360
Have you tried the medicine?

108
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,830
I have administered medicine,

109
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:47,360
but the effect is not great.

110
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,040
Perhaps,

111
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:51,190
acupuncture can make it work faster.

112
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,630
Then apply the needles quickly.

113
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,390
Well...

114
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,250
The acupuncture points

115
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,510
are all major points on a female's body.

116
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:00,010
She is a noble princess

117
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,570
and is to marry His Majesty.

118
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:04,320
It is inappropriate for me to do so.

119
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:05,920
It seems

120
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:07,650
we have to ask her for help.

121
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:22,040
You've packed your things so quickly?

122
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,430
Yes.

123
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,210
I'm leaving tomorrow.

124
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,330
Can you do me a favor?

125
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,870
It's not time for acupuncture
until tonight.

126
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,799
What's the rush?

127
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,730
Her Highness is ill.

128
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:41,750
We are departing tomorrow.

129
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:43,280
With her in this condition,

130
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,940
I'm afraid there will be problems
on our way.

131
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:57,670
Since you took care of me yesterday,

132
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,960
I will help you one more time.

133
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,040
Thank you.

134
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:24,130
Physician Han,

135
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:26,100
how is Her Highness's condition?

136
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:28,210
She is much better,

137
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:30,630
but it can't be cured
in one or two sessions.

138
00:09:30,630 --> 00:09:32,030
Her Highness's current condition

139
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,510
may delay our arrival in the capital.

140
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,570
I'm afraid we can't depart tomorrow.

141
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,540
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

142
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,770
Physician Han.

143
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:42,710
Wait a moment.

144
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:44,930
Pass down my order.

145
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,560
Tomorrow,

146
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,430
we'll depart as planned.

147
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,080
I'll go prepare.

148
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:57,910
Why must you go to the capital?

149
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,790
I told you, I'm going to save someone.

150
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:01,910
Save whom?

151
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:03,770
My second uncle's son.

152
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,080
His name is Han Mo.

153
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:07,200
He is the only male in our Han family.

154
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:10,470
He is currently locked
in the capital's death row.

155
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,360
What crime did he commit?

156
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,240
I don't know.

157
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:16,600
We lost contact many years ago.

158
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,870
Pack up and leave tomorrow.

159
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,720
Got it.

160
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,750
I'll return to Changmo tomorrow.

161
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:28,550
I mean,

162
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:31,950
you're going back to the capital
with us tomorrow.

163
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:38,870
Actually,

164
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:40,510
if you give me a few more days,

165
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:41,670
I can cure her.

166
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,750
I know.

167
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:45,960
That's why I said we would leave tomorrow.

168
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:46,800
This way,

169
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:50,010
you have a reason
to go to the capital with us.

170
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:16,890
Physician Han,

171
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:19,200
are you going by carriage or on horseback?

172
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,000
On horseback.

173
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,650
Alright.

174
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,550
I've also prepared a carriage for you.

175
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,720
If you get tired,

176
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,200
you can go in and rest.

177
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,720
General Xiao, you're very thoughtful.

178
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,650
On this journey,

179
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,930
I'll leave Her Highness in your care.

180
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,330
Don't worry.

181
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,790
Lu Li.

182
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,040
Tianlang Pass

183
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:38,280
is in your hands now.

184
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:39,990
You must hold Tianlang Pass.

185
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,390
I

186
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:44,430
swear to defend Tianlang Pass
to the death.

187
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,720
Good. Good.

188
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,510
On such a good day,

189
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:26,240
to have you,
Lord Zhang and Lord Wang, grace

190
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:28,130
my humble abode is truly an honor.

191
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:30,000
Come on, let's have a drink, My Lords.

192
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,080
-Come on.
-Come on.

193
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,240
Lord Li,

194
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:40,670
the three of us
are all important officials

195
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:42,930
left by the late Emperor for His Majesty.

196
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,630
You don't need to be so polite.

197
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:47,240
I'd never have known otherwise.

198
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,630
Lord Li, your garden

199
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:51,480
is even grander than His Majesty's harem.

200
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:55,120
Not only are the flowers
in the courtyard beautiful,

201
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:59,270
but the "flowers" on the stage
are also very alluring.

202
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:04,550
Lord Zhang, you truly have great taste.

203
00:13:05,030 --> 00:13:06,150
These women

204
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,660
are all dancers I bought from Changmo

205
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:10,550
at a high price.

206
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:14,550
Each one is highly skilled
and worth a fortune.

207
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:17,550
The lead dancer, Yina,

208
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:21,870
is exceptionally beautiful and priceless.

209
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:27,030
These foreign dancers' performances

210
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:29,440
are truly distinctive.

211
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,910
These foreign women

212
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:33,000
were originally prepared for His Majesty.

213
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,400
But His Majesty is young,

214
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:37,670
and I fear he might forsake his ambition
and neglect state affairs.

215
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,240
However,

216
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:41,120
how can we miss out on such beauty?

217
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,390
So,

218
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,350
I was thinking

219
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:47,240
of offering these women to you, Lord Zhang

220
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,120
and Lord Wang.

221
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:52,120
Please do not decline, My Lords.

222
00:13:52,670 --> 00:13:53,630
Great. Great.

223
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,000
Come on.

224
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,910
Let's have another drink.

225
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:59,360
-Come on.
-Come on.

226
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,750
Lord Li

227
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,750
is indeed the youngest among us.

228
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:09,270
He is more far-sighted than us.

229
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,150
Yes, right.

230
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,790
Then, Lord Zhang,

231
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:16,480
which dancer have you taken a fancy to?

232
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:20,750
Good things are not about quantity,
but quality.

233
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:26,510
A person should value integrity,
not greed.

234
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,240
Understood.

235
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:29,550
Later,

236
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:31,730
I will send the lead dancer, Yina,

237
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:34,270
to your mansion.

238
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:35,750
Good.

239
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:40,440
I'll send the rest of the dancers

240
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,150
to your place, Lord Wang.

241
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,120
Good. Good.

242
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,480
I won't eat this.

243
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:50,480
I will follow your lead, My Lords.

244
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:53,790
Please guide me more.

245
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,360
Me too.

246
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,000
Lord Li and I

247
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,550
also hope you, Lord Zhang,

248
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:03,550
will guide us more in the future.

249
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,670
Okay.

250
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:06,550
Thanks for your trouble.

251
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:10,670
On this festive day,
beauty stays by our side.

252
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:13,790
Let's drink this cup together.

253
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:15,360
Come on.

254
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,240
-Come on.
-Come on.

255
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:18,120
-Let's drink.
-Let's drink.

256
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:28,910
What's wrong?

257
00:15:28,910 --> 00:15:30,310
Are you not feeling well?

258
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:31,390
No.

259
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:32,480
I haven't ridden a horse this long

260
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,150
in quite some time.

261
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,670
Do you want to rest in the carriage?

262
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:38,010
No need.

263
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:40,120
If you can ride a horse, so can I.

264
00:15:41,030 --> 00:15:41,510
Okay.

265
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:42,390
Hyah!

266
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,490
General,

267
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:54,160
Lord Fei,

268
00:15:54,550 --> 00:15:57,010
we've carefully checked the surroundings.

269
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,550
There is a carriage in the backyard,
but no one is in it.

270
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:01,440
There is nothing else suspicious.

271
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:01,960
Good.

272
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:03,440
Then go settle Her Highness down first.

273
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:03,840
Yes.

274
00:16:04,790 --> 00:16:05,320
Let's go.

275
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:21,650
Is this what they deem thorough checking?

276
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:35,210
Please have a seat, everyone.

277
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,320
Please sit.

278
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:42,080
Why are you here?

279
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,670
Xiao Chi, you're escorting
Her Highness to the capital.

280
00:16:45,670 --> 00:16:47,790
It must be an extremely exhausting,
long journey.

281
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:48,790
How could you not even

282
00:16:48,790 --> 00:16:50,030
get a good night's sleep?

283
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,790
So,

284
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:53,000
I've reserved this inn in advance,

285
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:55,120
so Xiao Chi and Lord Fei,

286
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:57,180
you can have a place to stay on the way.

287
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,960
That's very thoughtful of you, Ms. Tang.

288
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,890
You're welcome.

289
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,870
The rooms are also ready.

290
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,390
After everyone finishes eating,

291
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:04,480
you can rest early.

292
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,790
Then I won't disturb you all.

293
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:09,880
I'll go to the kitchen

294
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,540
and serve the delicious food.

295
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,640
It seems having Ms. Tang fond of you

296
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:26,000
does have its perks.

297
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:31,720
Then,

298
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:34,240
Physician Han, after your meal,

299
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,250
remember to see to
Her Highness's treatment.

300
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,030
Got it.

301
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:42,440
I'll tend to

302
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,510
both of you in turn.

303
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:53,510
I checked with a silver needle before.

304
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:54,640
You were poisoned.

305
00:17:54,830 --> 00:17:57,030
Although I don't know who poisoned you,

306
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,600
this incident has granted me

307
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,970
passage to the capital.

308
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,110
Why

309
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,600
are you going to the capital?

310
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,060
To save my long-lost brother.

311
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,860
Things in this world
are quite interesting.

312
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:14,310
We haven't seen each other
for so many years.

313
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:16,350
I wonder if he will still recognize me

314
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,480
when we meet again.

315
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:20,510
Perhaps,

316
00:18:21,270 --> 00:18:22,670
even if he recognizes me,

317
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:25,030
he wouldn't want to acknowledge me.

318
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,750
I don't understand what you're saying.

319
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:32,030
But still, thank you, Physician Han,

320
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,890
for treating Her Highness today.

321
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:35,270
No need.

322
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,460
By treating Her Highness,

323
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:40,010
General Xiao will give me
more medical fees.

324
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,000
Besides,

325
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,530
treating people for free is something

326
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,790
I've done before.

327
00:18:49,750 --> 00:18:50,280
Alright.

328
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:53,240
How are you feeling, Your Highness?

329
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:54,270
Much better.

330
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:56,030
Thank you, Physician Han.

331
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:57,400
After a few more acupuncture sessions,

332
00:18:57,400 --> 00:19:00,400
the toxins in your body
should be completely cleared.

333
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,750
Your medical skills are excellent,

334
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:03,960
and you are so dedicated.

335
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,690
If you were by my father's side,

336
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:08,510
I would beg him every day
to let you take my pulse.

337
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,910
Then wouldn't you
have to suffer every day?

338
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,350
Don't worry.

339
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:16,510
You are so beautiful and kind.

340
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,830
Even when you arrive in the capital,

341
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:18,920
as long as you need me,

342
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,680
you can have Jin Xi find me anytime.

343
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,140
Thank you, Physician Han.

344
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,680
Hearing you say this,

345
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,330
I feel much more at ease.

346
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:27,440
Then,

347
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:29,150
please rest, Your Highness.

348
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,680
I've cured Her Highness.

349
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,030
How do you plan to thank me?

350
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:41,920
You said

351
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:44,320
General Xiao would reward you handsomely.

352
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:47,750
However,

353
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:51,000
we will still have to trouble you
along the way.

354
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,550
How many years

355
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:55,370
of my medical fees will this sum cover?

356
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:14,300
Physician Han.

357
00:20:16,030 --> 00:20:16,790
Tonight,

358
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,510
you're pressing a little too hard
with the needles.

359
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:22,440
I've never inserted the needles
too harshly, not once.

360
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:25,160
Perhaps General Xiao,
you're afraid of pain.

361
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:31,640
How could I be afraid of pain?

362
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,960
It's better if you're not.

363
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:33,960
Starting today,

364
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:36,030
I'll give you a massage after acupuncture.

365
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,200
It might hurt more.

366
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:39,080
You'll have to endure it.

367
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:41,970
Massage?

368
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,240
How do you do that?

369
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:49,000
It means with these hands,

370
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,590
I use varied force

371
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:52,830
to press,

372
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:54,110
lift,

373
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:55,440
knead,

374
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:56,830
and rub your body.

375
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,590
You will

376
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:00,200
place your hands on my body?

377
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:00,750
Yes.

378
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:03,480
Directly massage your body with my hands.

379
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:05,900
Well...

380
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:06,830
Why?

381
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,800
Are you afraid I'll hurt you?

382
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:10,920
That's not what I meant.

383
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,170
It's just...

384
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,640
I've never let a woman

385
00:21:16,070 --> 00:21:17,030
touch my body.

386
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,350
I've only ever practiced
locating acupoints

387
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:21,070
on wooden mannequins.

388
00:21:21,310 --> 00:21:23,160
It's my first time trying it
on a real person too.

389
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,240
It's both our first time.

390
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:24,830
I'm not shy.

391
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:25,920
Why should you be?

392
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,920
-I just...
-Xiao Chi!

393
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:34,160
Miss Tang?

394
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,020
Why is she here?

395
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:37,310
How should I know?

396
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:39,520
Ask her yourself when she comes in.

397
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:41,270
She loves you so much

398
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,920
and has taken such good care of everyone.

399
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,070
She wants to see you.

400
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,270
Shouldn't you hurry up and see

401
00:21:45,270 --> 00:21:46,440
what she wants?

402
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:48,750
Well, at least wait until I get dressed.

403
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:49,350
Oh.

404
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:51,630
General Xiao, are you being shy?

405
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:52,630
It's fine.

406
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:54,110
You'll grow accustomed
to repeated meetings.

407
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,270
It's normal to be shy the first time.

408
00:21:55,270 --> 00:21:56,670
You'll be fine next time.

409
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,030
Xiao Chi.

410
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:02,150
Just a moment, Miss Tang.

411
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,030
Come in.

412
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,510
What is it?

413
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,030
Oh.

414
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:17,830
Physician Han, you're here too.

415
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:20,270
I was treating your beloved Xiao Chi.

416
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:21,750
Mm.

417
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:24,880
Thanks for your hard work, Physician Han.

418
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:25,920
Xiao Chi,

419
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:28,000
I specifically made
some ginseng soup for you.

420
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,200
Thank you, Miss Tang.

421
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,770
Just leave it there.

422
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:39,590
Then I'll trouble you

423
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:41,440
to watch Xiao Chi

424
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:43,310
drink this bowl of soup.

425
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:49,070
This ginseng soup is quite good.

426
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,640
But it's a pity.

427
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:53,480
Xiao Chi can only have regular food now,

428
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:54,790
no medicinal tonics.

429
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:55,960
I'm tired today too.

430
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:57,230
I'll have it instead.

431
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:03,110
The heat was a bit off.

432
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,170
Simmer it longer next time.

433
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:08,530
You drank my soup, yet you still complain.

434
00:23:08,830 --> 00:23:10,200
If there's nothing else,

435
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,600
Miss Tang, you may leave.

436
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,200
If you fail to cure Xiao Chi,

437
00:23:20,270 --> 00:23:22,730
be careful—
I might slip you some laxatives.

438
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,270
She's left.

439
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:36,920
So,

440
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:38,750
are we still doing the massage?

441
00:23:38,750 --> 00:23:39,550
Of course.

442
00:23:40,590 --> 00:23:41,450
I was thinking,

443
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:42,590
maybe

444
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:43,720
you could do it over my clothes.

445
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:44,650
Absolutely not.

446
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:45,830
Through your clothes,

447
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:48,110
I can't find the exact acupoints

448
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:49,880
or control my strength.

449
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:52,590
I-I just think...

450
00:23:52,590 --> 00:23:53,680
Stop dawdling.

451
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,080
Lie prone.

452
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,500
The General is going to suffer again.

453
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:44,350
I'm so exhausted.

454
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:46,270
It seems practicing on wooden mannequins

455
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:48,600
doesn't help me control my strength well.

456
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:57,120
I don't know who howled
outside last night,

457
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,790
keeping me up all night.

458
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:03,240
You look quite well.

459
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:05,340
Did you sleep well last night?

460
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,100
I slept quite well last night.

461
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:09,030
I didn't hear any howling.

462
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:11,240
You must have misheard, Zheng.

463
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:14,920
Ms. Tang,

464
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:17,310
are you here to see off General Xiao?

465
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:17,880
Yes.

466
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,060
To see off Xiao Chi,

467
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:21,270
and also to see you off, Lord Fei Zheng.

468
00:25:21,270 --> 00:25:23,070
Then we'll meet again next time.

469
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:29,960
It seems we won't have to
worry about lodgings ahead.

470
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,920
Where is the carriage?

471
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,400
My back aches.

472
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:38,110
Then take the carriage today.

473
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:42,400
No,

474
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,330
I'd better ride a horse.

475
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:49,740
Your Highness.

476
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:51,410
Your Highness.

477
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:53,630
Let's set off.

478
00:25:58,750 --> 00:25:59,280
Let's go.

479
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,030
Tomorrow,

480
00:26:04,110 --> 00:26:05,570
we will reach the capital.

481
00:26:39,270 --> 00:26:40,270
At this speed,

482
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:43,010
we can arrive in the capital tomorrow.

483
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,490
Thinking of seeing Liu Chu,

484
00:26:47,310 --> 00:26:49,790
I have an indescribable feeling
in my heart.

485
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,110
By the way,

486
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:53,790
along the way,

487
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,660
I noticed Lord Fei
looking at you strangely.

488
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:59,240
Did you two know each other before?

489
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,470
How is that possible?

490
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:04,270
He is an official of Jinglan.

491
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:07,040
He must have lived
in Jinglan since childhood.

492
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,000
Moreover,

493
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,960
for all these years, I

494
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:11,430
have never left Changmo.

495
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:12,790
How could I know him?

496
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:17,830
Anyway, I think he's a bit weird.

497
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,370
Don't overthink it.

498
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:22,610
Let me help you get to bed early.

499
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,260
Physician Han,

500
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:42,510
I thought

501
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:45,030
Her Highness required
no treatment this evening.

502
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,000
I came to you.

503
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:47,240
Me?

504
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:50,920
We will arrive in the capital tomorrow.

505
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,490
After we part this time,

506
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:55,750
it'll probably be hard
for us to meet again.

507
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:59,590
I want to hear you tell the truth.

508
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,720
What truth?

509
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:10,750
Are you really the Jin Xi I know?

510
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:26,370
There are many people
with the same name in the world.

511
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:29,160
I am definitely not the person you know.

512
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,550
After all,

513
00:28:30,790 --> 00:28:32,990
I have served Her Highness since I was 5.

514
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,600
You've got the wrong person.

515
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,200
Fine.

516
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:38,310
Then consider my efforts wasted.

517
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:41,650
Physician Han.

518
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:47,200
Thank you.

519
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:11,550
My Lady,

520
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,820
calling me here late at night,

521
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:15,720
do you have any orders?

522
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:21,480
Seeing this token

523
00:29:21,750 --> 00:29:23,880
is the same as beholding the King of Mo.

524
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,510
You've recognized me?
